{"tid":1692880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【全民DEL FACEBOOK】　Facebook 幫中共，打壓香港人自由","createTime":"2019-11-04T09:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:19:23.000Z","uid":14328,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"769e101dc13e4d69fbd423d6303ab0b7bd5a72a2","tid":1692880,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/11/04/AtqlOd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F11%2F04%2FAtqlOd.png&h=6fba94ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張相，你試下放上Facebook<br />\n輕則Del相、無得Share<br />\n重則BAM Account<br />\n<br />\n唔信自己試下<br />\n<br />\n香港人應立即聯合外國，全球，發動 #boycottfacebook<br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格奶共奶到出哂面，老婆又係中國人，個仔又隊比習近平叫佢幫手改名<br />\n目的只在進入中國市場<br />\n<br />\n柒就柒在<br />\n明明中國市場都已經入唔到<br />\n仲要幫中國做技術支援<br />\n賣用戶資料呢啲可能已經做緊<br />\n<br />\n全球用戶個人私隱危在旦夕！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全香港人立即Del Facebook，轉用Twitter，如果連呢樣野都做唔到，更加大既突破仲點做落去？</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce4979e7a4079319b4640ec11daeeb571bf5f675","tid":1692880,"uid":14328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:47:19.000Z","msg":"無人理　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔講Twitter香港水軍我幾千人<br />\n<br />\n香港人連DEL 奶共FACEBOOK都做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n你每日手機既相、大頭照，可能通過facebook 每日上緊去大陸Server呀屌！"},{"pid":"4acec03caec2f5f8c91a46a7f2831ad022c217b3","tid":1692880,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔講Twitter香港水軍<span style=\"color: red;\">得</span>幾千人<br />\n<br />\n香港人連DEL 奶共FACEBOOK都做唔到？<br />\n<br />\n你每日手機既相、大頭照，可能通過facebook 每日上緊去大陸Server呀屌！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"16fabd55560d9b7f0f15e1e769688054e5d756b3","tid":1692880,"uid":138916,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:47:57.00